# Drop free-license statusbar textures (.tga, .blp, .png) here for PUBLIC registration.
# Then add a registerPublic("statusbar", "ShortName", PUBLIC_ASSETS .. [[statusbars\file.tga]])
# line in _registerPublicStatusbars() inside Cairn-Media-1.0.lua.
# Public = visible to Cairn consumers AND registered with LibSharedMedia-3.0
# under "Cairn <ShortName>" (so WeakAuras / ElvUI / Details! / etc. see it).
